# Module 3 - Conditions
## Level 5 - Challenge 1

Problem
Write a program to check whether a year is a leap year.

Instructions
1. Ask the user to enter a year.
2. A year is a leap year if it is divisible by 4.
3. Print "Leap Year" if true.
4. Otherwise print "Not a Leap Year".

Example Input
2024

Example Output
Leap Year

Hint
Use the modulo operator % to check divisibility.

Broken Code
year = int(input("Enter year: "))
if year % 4 = 0:
print("Leap Year")
else
print("Not a Leap Year")

Correct Code
year = int(input("Enter year: "))
if year % 4 == 0:
    print("Leap Year")
else:
    print("Not a Leap Year")
